case_body_condition: Not recognizable - Near complete or complete skeleton
case_circumstances:
The victim's skeletal remains were discovered in a wooded ravine off Franklin Road near Spencer in rural Owen County. The bones were found by a man who was preparing to build a home on the site.

Spencer is about 40 miles southwest of Indianapolis.
